{"tid":786953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子中大女廁偷拍被撤控不誠實取用電腦罪","createTime":"2018-08-20T09:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T11:27:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"80650db6eab565c2c5402b21578a1be56dd2c79b","tid":786953,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1413459_1_L_20180820172606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1413459_1_L_20180820172606.jpg&h=231344ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名30歲男子在中文大學偷拍女性如廁，被控遊蕩導致他人擔心，以及目的在於使其本人或他人不誠實地獲益而取用電腦罪，在沙田裁判法院提堂。但控方有鑑於早前高院法官指律政司告錯罪，控方申請撤控不誠實取用電腦罪，署理主任裁判官王詩麗接納撤控。<br />\n<br />\n至於被告承認的遊蕩導致他人擔心罪，押後至今年9月7日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n案情指今年2月2日，一名女子在中大綜合教學樓女廁如廁時，見到鄰廁有手伸出，拿著手機拍攝，她隨即呼叫並報警求助。警員拘捕被告，他承認尾隨受害人入女廁及偷拍，被發現後逃走並把有關片段刪除。"},{"pid":"dcdd031e8ffb9f264ed92f5554839c76022b1bd2","tid":786953,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T10:50:41.000Z","msg":"真空期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc33e85dcacb9652672f99aec9d4a2b6c32da181","tid":786953,"uid":18772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"條友應該有d背景照住<br />\n改判無罪釋放啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7fd51310169b764929b70d3fcd26eb8598d363","tid":786953,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:20:30.000Z","msg":"佢地都濫用得耐啦呢條罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868c50a5b80c57e1a32e1b941df25e6cf7b7eef8","tid":786953,"uid":171107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:22:17.000Z","msg":"如果用菲林相機係咪入唔到呢條罪"},{"pi